ne\r\n10. ganti warning light, sirine dan pasang sumpump \r\n11. Cek floating switch (akses terhalang peralatan, kabel dilepas)\r\n12. Ganti submersible pump/pasang potable, ganti warning light dan sirine\r\n13. Ganti submersible pump/pasang potable, ganti sirine dan warning light, repaint panel\r\n14. Pengecekan sumpump eksisiting', 'Sudah Dikerjakan', 'None'),
